      "content": "It's best to frame this as a proactive finding during a routine audit, focusing on rapid remediation rather than the exposure itself. You can state that a specific, non-sensitive data bucket was temporarily misconfigured, and the issue was identified and patched immediately. Emphasize that the breach was contained quickly and that security protocols were immediately reviewed to prevent recurrence, showcasing your responsive commitment to user data.",
